                            Forschungsumgebung / Beta maṣāḥǝft,  Akademie der Wissenschaften in Hamburg</dc:publisher><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu"/><dcterms:bibliographicCitation>LIT7098QeneAlam</dcterms:bibliographicCitation><dc:format>xml</dc:format><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">en</dc:language><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">gez</dc:language><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">sv</dc:language><dc:contributor>Alessandro Bausi</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Jonas Karlsson</dc:contributor><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/ChristianLiterature"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Poetry"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Qene"/><dc:title>ʿĀlam ʾǝska gizehā ba-ḥabla zǝngāʾe tǝsǝḥǝbanni
          wa-tāwarrǝdanni kāʾǝba ḫaba za-qadāmi margam (Qǝne possibly of the śəllāse-type)</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ዓለም፡ እስከ፡ ጊዜሃ፡ በሐብለ፡ ዝንጋኤ፡ ትስሕበኒ፡ ወታወርደኒ፡ ካእበ፡ ኀበ፡ ዘቀዳሚ፡ መርገም፤</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ʿĀlam ʾǝska gizehā ba-ḥabla zǝngāʾe tǝsǝḥǝbanni wa-tāwarrǝdanni kāʾǝba ḫaba za-qadāmi margam (Qǝne possibly of the śǝllāse-type)</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Until the world suddenly drags and pulls me down again to the first curse with the cord of delirium…</dc:title><dc:source rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppQ1524o"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam"><lawd:hasAttestation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppQ1524o"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam"><saws:isAttributedToAuthor rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14579WaldaGabreel"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14579WaldaGabreel"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Walda Gabrǝʾel</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7098QeneAlam/title/t1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ዓለም፡ እስከ፡ ጊዜሃ፡ በሐብለ፡ ዝንጋኤ፡ ትስሕበኒ፡ ወታወርደኒ፡ ካእበ፡ ኀበ፡ ዘቀዳሚ፡ መርገም፤</rdfs:label></rdf:Description></rdf:RDF>